Christian Louboutin
Louix Ray Spiked PVC Covered High-Top Sneakers
Brand New w/ OUT Original Box
Handcrafted in Italy
MSRP  $1,295.00

Size:  45 EU (label); 12 US Men's (CLB size chart); 11 UK (CLB size chart)
Material:  40% Textile fibres, 30% Leather, 30% Various Materials
Details:  PVC coated leather with patent leather trim; Luxurious, silver, supple calfskin leather lining; Spikes all-over; Round patent leather pouch with raised logo; Red bottoms (of course)
Packaging:  Original box is NOT included;  Will be shipped in a non-clb box for safe delivery.

Christian Louboutin's 'Louix Ray' sneakers are a toughened-up take on the designer's signature high-top style. They're made using PVC that has a smoky, transparent appearance and detailed all over with spiked embellishments.  As a brand, Christian Louboutin is synonymous with elegance, technical proficiency, and of course, that iconic red sole.  Elevate your ultra-luxury sneaker game with the Christian Louboutin Arpoador Mesh & Suede Sneaker - a versatile and luxurious addition to any wardrobe.

BRAZILIAN BY NAME, COOL BY NATURE:  Born from Christian’s enduring love of Brazil and named after the iconic rock and surf spot situated between the beaches of Copacabana and Ipanema, the new Arpoador sneaker is the latest style to join the Maison’s iconic sneaker collection. And while its versatile dynamic silhouette nods to the graceful movements of Capoeira and the contours of renowned Brazilian architect Oscar Niemeyer's work, its complex technical construction has Christian Louboutin written all over it.

STAND OUT IN STYLE:  whether dressed up or dressed down, there's an Arpoador out there for every personality. First launched worldwide in our iconic Louboutin red, the latest addition to their sneaker collection now comes in a variety of colors, for both men and women.
